{"tid":959394,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭祝劉德華12月演唱會成功","createTime":"2018-12-28T14:03:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-29T05:37:45.000Z","uid":5195,"like":84,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"c7dd4b82496a6955ab39e1232b335d0c8199d1c1","tid":959394,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T14:03:43.000Z","msg":"有「民間特首」之稱的劉德華，早前為團結香港基金撐填海宣傳短片擔任旁白，更罕有表態支持港府在東大嶼興建大規模人工島，結果遭到網民圍攻。行政長官林鄭月娥今日在施政報告記者會上倒過來挺「劉華」，澄清短片同施政報告內容近似是巧合，「無同劉先生夾過」，又指自己和劉德華年紀差不多，出身背景又相似，支持填海都是為了下一代，對劉被人身攻擊感不值，又預祝劉德華12月演唱會成功。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/W8grW8b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW8grW8b.jpg&h=487d7616&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6d70a541d0f40f5240594666c6c851f70f12bef3","tid":959394,"uid":151534,"like":59,"dislike":0,"score":59,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T14:11:56.000Z","msg":"即刻燈到腰斬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6042f3ea7e05b970c6303f356321fdae5b39b104","tid":959394,"uid":29080,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T14:13:24.000Z","msg":"經佢把口加持都會收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上次有#metoo"},{"pid":"cf9b70e619bf280a38fbaaa10cc5d86f627d66c5","tid":959394,"uid":20816,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T14:15:32.000Z","msg":"人善不失聲<br />\n簡單一個道理"},{"pid":"87a80c2493c7579bf04cba84899874548c0098c8","tid":959394,"uid":6799,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T14:15:53.000Z","msg":"燈死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi